Elan Says It Will Pay About $12 Million to Buy Back Senior Bonds

-- B y   P a u l   A r m s t r o n g
-- 
2011-10-17T11:15:10Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/elan-says-it-will-pay-about-12-million-to-buy-back-senior-bonds.html
Elan Corporation Plc said it will
pay about $12 million to buy back senior notes issued by its
subsidiaries.  The company will repurchase $4 million of its 2013 fixed-
rate notes; $7.3 million of 2013 floating-rate notes; and
$500,000 of its 2016 senior notes, it said in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Armstrong at 
 parmstrong10@bloomberg.net  